            "heading": "Est Alvarez Barberia",
            "content": "<div class=\"m-store-info\">\n  <div class=\"m-store-info__item\">\n      <h4>Dirección</h4>\n      <p class=\"m:text-color-subtext\">\n        Estrella #32, V. Carranza<br>\n        Cuahutémoc, Nativitas, Tlaxcala\n      </p>\n      <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Estrella+%2332,+Cuahut%C3%A9moc,+Nativitas,+Tlaxcala\" target=\"_blank\">\n        Cómo llegar\n      </a>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"m-store-info__item\">\n      <h4 class=\"h5\">Horarios</h4>\n      <p class=\"m:text-color-subtext\">\n        Lunes a sábado<br>\n        11:00 AM a 7:00 PM\n      </p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"m-store-info__item\">\n      <h4 class=\"h5\">Contáctanos</h4>\n      <p class=\"m:text-color-subtext\">\n        Escríbenos por WhatsApp y te atenderemos<br>\n        lo antes posible.\n      </p>\n      <p>\n        <a href=\"https://wa.me/5215614622363\" target=\"_blank\">+52 1 56 1462 2363</a>\n      </p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"m-store-info__item\">\n      <h4 class=\"h5\">Redes Sociales</h4>\n      <ul>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61557400600163\" target=\"_blank\">\n            Facebook\n          </a>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n  </div>\n</div>",
            "width": "50%"
          }
        },
